---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Get Started" 
  description="Access Vizino Studio - Sign up, login, or try guest mode"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Get Started with Vizino Studio</h1>
    <p>Multiple ways to begin your AI-powered design journey</p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2>Three Ways to Get Started</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3>üöÄ Guest Mode (Instant Access)</h3>
        <p><strong>Try before you commit</strong></p>
        <p>Explore Vizino Studio's features without registration. Perfect for trying the platform and seeing what's possible.</p>
        <a href="https://vizino-studio.com" class="button" target="_blank">Launch Guest Mode</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3>üìù Sign Up (Free Account)</h3>
        <p><strong>Unlock full potential</strong></p>
        <p>Create a free account to save projects, manage multiple spaces, and track your V Points balance.</p>
        <a href="https://vizino-studio.com/signup" class="button" target="_blank">Create Account</a>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card" style="text-align: center;">
        <h3>üîë Log In (Existing User)</h3>
        <p><strong>Welcome back</strong></p>
        <p>Already have an account? Sign in to access your projects, saved designs, and usage history.</p>
        <a href="https://vizino-studio.com/login" class="button" target="_blank">Log In</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="background: #f9f9f9; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    
    <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h3>Do I need to sign up to use Vizino Studio?</h3>
      <p>No! Guest mode allows you to try all core features without registration. Sign up to save your projects and access advanced features like custom API keys.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h3>What are V Points?</h3>
      <p>V Points are credits used for generative AI actions. Free credits are included when you sign up. You can also integrate your own API key for extended usage without additional costs.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h3>How do I manage my API key?</h3>
      <p>Once logged in, visit your user profile settings to add, update, or remove API keys. This allows you to use Vizino Studio with your own generative AI account.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h3>Can I organize my designs?</h3>
      <p>Yes! Create projects and add multiple spaces to each project. This helps you organize designs by client, property, or project type.</p>
    </div>

    <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
      <h3>Is there an onboarding tour?</h3>
      <p>Absolutely! New users get an interactive onboarding tour that walks you through the key features and how to use them effectively.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 3rem;">
    <h2>System Requirements</h2>
    <p>Vizino Studio is a web-based application that works in any modern browser:</p>
    <ul style="margin-left: 2rem; margin-top: 1rem;">
      <li>Modern web browser (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)</li>
      <li>Stable internet connection</li>
      <li>JavaScript enabled</li>
      <li>Minimum screen resolution: 768px width recommended</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); color: white; border-radius: 8px;">
    <h2 style="color: white; border-bottom-color: white;">Need Help Getting Started?</h2>
    <p>Check our contact page for support options or reach out to our team</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="button" style="background: white; color: #667eea;">Contact Us</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
